==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Illure
<hw>Il*lure"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>il-</ets> in + <ets>lure</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deceive; to entice;
to lure.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The devil insnareth the souls of many men, by <qex>illuring</qex>
them with the muck and dung of this world.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>ill-usage</ent>⟦br⟧
